le rire et la comédie. Bref...

474
00:24:12,057 --> 00:24:14,933
- Des vacances.
- Quoi ? Non!

475
00:24:15,065 --> 00:24:16,278
Je parle...

476
00:24:16,279 --> 00:24:17,900
d'un cassage!

477
00:24:18,345 --> 00:24:19,799
De Michael Scott.

478
00:24:20,471 --> 00:24:23,557
